/*
    This file defines types, which pokemon and moves have.

    types: A list of all types

    typeModifiers: Defines type multipliers.
        The format is [move type, defending pokemon type, multiplier].
        For example, ["Water", "Fire", 2.0] defines water moves as doing
        2x damage to fire pokemon
*/

